title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 28 2022

description:
GOP nominee for governor in Pennsylvania, Doug Mastriano, joins Clay and Buck during the final stretch. CNN paints Pelosi attacker as right-wing extremist. GOP Senate nominee General Don Bolduc joins Clay and Buck, and could be the difference maker in the Senate. Guaranteed to send chills up your spine: C&B's go-to Halloween movies.
